.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, badminton
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, german
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Sport   | badminton            | soccer    |
| Nationality   | australian     | german   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

